reviews.text:
Trying this in a kayfun 5 tank after a 2 month steep .... i forgot i mixed it ;)&#xD;
Ofc the red burley takes the all round taste to me with the turkish blending in aswell, im tasting the toffee and praline but not too much its just right under the tabaccos and then theres the granny smith just and only just keeping its head above it all.&#xD;
Great mix again fear im really enjoying this one in fact id say its on par with ABUELA .&#xD;
For just under 6% flavoring this is full of flavor and has to be tried, 100ml getting made later thats for sure 5 stars!!!
